                        <interp inst="t18680127-208-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been convicted in De<lb></lb>cember</hi>, 1861, <hi rend="italic">when he was imprisoned One Year; to this he</hi>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.**—<hi rend="italic">
